  FILTER ( ?RotatableBondCountValue > 0 && ?RotatableBondCountValue < 2 )

}

  ?Species os:hasHydrogenBondAcceptorCount/os:value ?HydrogenBondAcceptorCountValue .
  FILTER ( ?HydrogenBondAcceptorCountValue > -0.1 && ?HydrogenBondAcceptorCountValue < 0.1 )
  ?Species os:hasBondChiralDefCount/os:value ?BondChiralDefCountValue .
  FILTER ( ?BondChiralDefCountValue > -1.0 && ?BondChiralDefCountValue < 1.0 )
  ?Species os:hasRotatableBondCount ?RotatableBondCount .
  ?Species os:hasAtomChiralUndefCount ?AtomChiralUndefCount .
}

  FILTER ( ?ExactMassValue > 145.767519 )
  ?Species os:hasChemicalClass/rdfs:label "dichlorophenol" .

  ?Species os:hasChemicalClass/rdfs:label "molecule" .

  FILTER ( ?HenrysLawConstantValue < 1 )
}

question: Search for chemical species in the chemical entity class that have a minimum solubility of 0.045899999999999996, an approximate logS of -3.7 and a maximum mono isotopic weight of 279.50373.

query.sparql:
SELECT ?Species WHERE {
  ?Species os:hasChemicalClass/rdfs:label "chemical entity" .
  ?Species os:hasSolubility/os:value ?SolubilityValue .
  FILTER ( ?SolubilityValue >= 0.045899999999999996 )
  ?Species os:hasLogS/os:value ?LogSValue .
  FILTER ( ?LogSValue > -3.7*1.1 && ?LogSValue < -3.7*0.9 )
  ?Species os:hasMonoIsotopicWeight/os:value ?MonoIsotopicWeightValue .
  FILTER ( ?MonoIsotopicWeightValue <= 279.50373 )
}

question: What is the total Gibbs free energy and NHOMO energy of Tc across all basis set

  ?HOMOMinus1Energy a occ:HOMOMinus1Energy .

}

SELECT ?Species WHERE {
  ?Species os:hasAtomChiralDefCount/os:value ?AtomChiralDefCountValue .
  FILTER ( ?AtomChiralDefCountValue > -1 )
  ?Species os:hasMolecularWeight/os:value ?MolecularWeightValue .

  FILTER ( ?BondChiralDefCountValue = 0.0 )
  ?Species os:hasBondChiralCount/os:value ?BondChiralCountValue .
  FILTER ( ?BondChiralCountValue > -0.1 && ?BondChiralCountValue < 0.1 )
}
